# If you get "Not Found" errors in chat or API calls fail:
# 1. Ensure the backend is running: python launch.py (or uvicorn in backend/)
# 2. Ensure you access the app via http://localhost:5173 (Vite dev server with proxy)
# 3. If proxy still fails, create .env with:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8000/api
